manhattan.template

クラス Station

  • java.lang.Object
    • manhattan.template.Station
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    java.lang.Comparable<Station>

    public class Station
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Station>

    Information of station

    consisting of
    Station name, HorizontalPosition, Station network

    This class is IMMUTABLE.

    Station name and network name must be 8 or less letters. If the network name is 'DSM', comparison of networks between instances is not done, station name and horizontal position is considered.
    バージョン:
    0.0.5
    作成者:
    kensuke
